STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Robert L. EVANS, Defendant-Movant. M-30 Sept. Term 2018
079144 Supreme Court of New Jersey. October 10, 2018

ORDER

It is ORDERED that the motion for reconsideration is granted in part, and the matter is remanded to the Superior Court, Appellate Division for further proceedings consistent with the Court's corrected opinion.
